<DOCHDR>
http://www.cei.org:80/ebb/suprfund.html 207.33.42.44 19970101101250 text/html 7297
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 10:13:01 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 7126
