<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>The Competitive Enterprise Institute</TITLE>
<META Name="description" Content="A pro-market, public policy group
committed to advancing the principles of free enterprise and limited
government.">
<META Name="keywords" Content="free-market environmentalism regulation libertarian conservative environment free-market environmentalism regulation libertarian conservative  environment free-market environmentalism regulation libertarian conservative  environment free-market environmentalism regulation libertarian conservative">
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#009900" VLINK="#000099">

<TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=600 CELLPADDING=5>
<TR><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=260 ROWSPAN=2>

<TABLE BORDER=7 CELLPADDING=5 ALIGN=CENTER>
<TR><TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFDD">
<CENTER>
<FONT SIZE=+1 COLOR="#000099"><B>Competitive Enterprise Institute</B></FONT><P>
<FONT SIZE=-1><B><A HREF="/about.html">About CEI</A> | <A HREF="/policy.html">Public Policy</A> | <A HREF="/quote.html">Quote</A> | <A HREF="/sellout.html">Sellout</A></B></FONT>

<P>
<FONT SIZE="-1">December 30, 1996</FONT><P>
<FONT SIZE=+2><I>Highlights
&amp; Updates:</I></FONT><P>

<A HREF="/update/1296-rd.html">Legalized Gambling<BR> in the United States</A><BR> by Robert R. Detlefsen <!-- 12/26 --><P>

<A HREF="/pubs/gsources.html">New <I>Free Market Environmental Bibliography</I> now available</A> <!-- 12/26 --><P>

<A HREF="/brookes/engler1.html">Dinner address by<BR>
Governor John Engler</A> <!-- 12/19 --><P>

<A HREF="/update/1196-ja.html">No Basis in Reality</A><BR> by Jonathan Adler <!-- 12/4 --><P>

<A HREF="/update/1196-sk.html">Air Bags</A><BR> by Sam Kazman <!-- 12/4 --><P>

<A HREF="/update/1196-bl.html">The Power of Positive Drinking</A><BR> by Ben Lieberman <!-- 12/2 --><P>

<A HREF="/releases/96-11-15.html">Population Control Won't Stop World Hunger</A> <!-- 11/20 --><P>

<A HREF="/essays/adler2.html">Greens' Bark Worse Than Bite:<BR> Environmental Issues Played Minor Role in Congressional
Races</A> <!-- 11/6 --><P>


<BR>
<A HREF="http://www2.eff.org/blueribbon.html"><IMG SRC="/images/ribbon.gif" height=69 width=43 border=0 ALT="Internet Free Speech Campaign"></A><BR>
