<DOCOLDNO>IA002-000017-B022-89</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cei.org:80/agpap7.html 207.33.42.44 19970101102657 text/html 8071
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wed, 01 Jan 1997 10:27:07 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Content-length: 7900
