Transparency,&#148; in <i>The Greening of World Trade</i>, p. 124.  EC
provisions allowing environmental trade restrictions are modeled after
GATT&#146;s general exceptions provision.  Many of the same individuals who
interpret these provisions on the European Court of Justice serve frequently on
GATT dispute settlement panels (p. 118).<p>
