There are two major reasons why your business can benefit today from CommunityNetwork's Internet and World Wide Web services:<BR>
<UL>
<LI><B>Our fees are way below market costs</B>---only $95 total for six
months service for our business Web Page. Compare this to Internet service providers charging up to $5000 in design and set-up fees, and $50 per month storage. Our Web Page design is a low-cost turn-key method for small businesses to utilize Internet services --- and Internet advantages.
</UL>
<UL>
<LI><B>CommunityNetwork continuously develops and improves links</B> to direct
people on the Internet and World Wide Web to <B>your</B> Business Home Pages.
Any Internet service can post your business's Home Page, but CommunityNetwork
directs potentially interested Internet and World Wide Web traffic to your
Business Home Page(s).  CommunityNetwork will hook your Page(s) to the most
popular Internet searches, and seek out other related Information Home Pages
where your potential customers may be browsing.
</UL>
<BR>
Here at Community Network, we are always thinking of ways to take advantage of new technologies and develop sites which will let our customers (and visitors to our sites!)  enjoy the maximum capabilities of the internet.  For example, we have big plans for "Shockwave," which will enable visitors to not only view features of your home page through scanned-in photos or professional graphics, but to hear them as well.  Show potential customers the view of the ocean from your motel room, and enhance it with a sound byte of the waves on the shore! Entice customers to your Victorian B&B with a byte of the Brandenburg Concertos.  The possibilities are endless!
</TD>
