<H1><IMG SRC="Drown1.gif">       Drown Agency            </H1>

<HR>
<H2>Phone  </H2>

<H3>207-646-7998 Res. </H3>

<H3>207-646-5131 Office </H3>

<H3>207-646-6719 Fax </H3>
The Drown Agency is one of Southern Maine's most renowned Real Estate office. Take 
a look and you can see we have some of the most beautiful homes in the area. We can 
find you the dream home, or second home, that you have always wanted. Our office 
is located on Route 1 right across from the Wells Junior High School. Here are some directions 
to get to us:<P>

<H3>From the South: </H3>
Go North on the Maine Turnpike (95 North). Get off on Exit 2/Wells. Turn left onto 
Route 9. Follow Route 9 until you reach Route 1 and then take a right on Route 1. 
We are about 1/2 mile South on Route 1 on the left hand side.<P>

<H3>From North: </H3>
Come down the Maine Turnpike (95 South). Get off on Exit 2/Wells. Turn left onto Route 
9. Follow Route 9 until you reach Route 1 and then take a right on Route 1. We are 
about 1/2 mile South on Route 1 on the left hand side.<P>
<center><IMG SRC="Drown2.gif"></center><P>
My name is Wendy Fitch. I would be glad to discuss any of the listings here, or any 
type of home you may desire. We may even have YOUR Dream House!<P>
<P>
Here are just a few of our fine listing:<P>

<CENTER><H5>Central Avenue  Wells, Maine</H5> <BR>
<IMG SRC="Drown3.gif"><P>
</CENTER>This first listing is a beautiful home with marsh views and distant ocean views. It 
is a large contemporary home with oak floors, wrap around decks and all with privacy! 
For more information/and the full listing click <a href="http://www.sirius.com/~fitch/drown/Listing1.html">here
</a>!<P>

<CENTER><H5>Island Beach Road     Wells, Maine </H5>  <BR><IMG SRC="Drown4.gif">
</CENTER><P>
This beautiful house is located on picturesque Drakes Island. This is a 5 bedroom 
condominium and is done in a contemporary theme. It has large windows for beautiful 
ocean and marsh views. The unit has 3 bathrooms and very large front and rear decks. 
To find out more click <a href="http://www.sirius.com/~fitch/drown/Listing2.html">here
</a>!<P>
<P>

<CENTER><H5>Atlantic Avenue   Wells, Maine </H5> <BR><IMG SRC="Drown5.gif"> 
</CENTER>This is a beautiful ocean front home located on Wells Beach. It is a 2 apartment beach 
house directly on sandy Wells Beach. It could easily be converted into a single family 
home. From this house you can see from <a href="http://www.communitynetwork.com/kport/kport.html">
Kennebunkport
</a> to <A href="http://www.communitynetwork.com/york/york.html">York</A>. It is a year round 
home with a great rental history. This house is selling with most of the furnishings. To see more about this property click <a href="http://www.sirius.com/~fitch/drown/Listing3.html">here
</a><P>

