			</TABLE>
</TD>
<TD Align=Left Valign=Top>
<CENTER>
<IMG WIDTH=119 HEIGHT=32 SRC="gifs/shorelands.gif"><P><FONT SIZE=-1><B>Idlease &amp; Shorelands Guest Resort</B></FONT><P></CENTER>
Shorelands is a relaxed Maine Cottage Resort. The way life used to be! We've grown gradually over the years and we are constantly adding improvements. Consequently our spotless cottages and apartments are all different in size and style. In any season, you'll find our prices moderate, and we have some great spring and fall packages. There's so much to do here at any time of year, and our location allows you to feel so close to everything, yet removed from noise and congestion. We're not posh . . . we're a friendly, family style resort that many guests come back to again and again for the quiet relaxed atmosphere, cleanliness, attentive service and Casual Country Comfort!<P>
