<h3>Full Country Reports</h3>

Business Europa publish full reports on a variety of countries in Central and Eastern Europe.  These can be purchased in paper form.  Please <a href="mailto:waldenpub@easynet.co.uk">contact us</a> for further details.<p>
An example of a report's content is shown here at this Web site:<p>
