1<html>
<head>
<title>Business Europa Briefing</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff" link="#FF0000" alink="#000000" vlink="#0000ff">

<center><i><font size=+2>S</font><font size=+1>ummer 1996.</i></font><br>

<img src="images/pinred.gif" alt="*"> <a href="bcmaced.html">Select Winter 1995</a></center>

<h3>MACEDONIA</h3>

Engineering consultants Alexander Gibb have won the EBRD funded project to design and then manage the modernisation of Skopje Airport.
<P>
New coal reserves have been discovered at the mining combine Oslomey. The estimated 13 million tonnes will be enough to keep the combine working for the next 15 years.

<p>
<hr>
<center><img src="images/pinred.gif" alt="*"> <a href="besummy1.html">Summary Menu</a></center>

</center>
<hr size=3>
