<body bgcolor="#ffffff" link="#FF0000" alink="#000000" vlink="#0000ff">

<P>
<a name="Top"></a>
<CENTER>
<h2>Natural Resources</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>
<ul>
<li> <a href="buseu10a.html">Production</a>
<li> <a href="buseu10b.html">Contribution to Economy</a>
</UL>
<P>
<center><IMG SRC="images/pinred.gif"> <A HREF="bsmenu.html">Bulgaria Subjects</A></center>
<P>
<hr>
<P>
Mineral deposits are varied but of generally low quality. Iron ore, and
lead zinc ore are mined at Kremikovtsi and there are substantial deposits of 
manganese ore at Obrochishte near Varna where reserves are estimated at more
than 120 million tonnes. Other iron ore deposits are found in Sofia, 
Chiporovtsi, Yambol, and Troyan. The iron ore near Sofia is made up of 
hematite, limonite and siderite with iron content varying from 23 to 46 per 
cent. The ore contains significant quantities of manganese, lead, copper and 
silver. Chromium mineralisations occur in the Rhodopi area of Southern 
Bulgaria. There is also a deposit of tungsten in the area of Gruncharitsa.
<P>
Non metal minerals include over 100,000 tonnes of refractory dolomites with 
a 20 per cent content of manganese oxides extracted each year. Proven 
reserves are over 60 million tonnes. Proven reserves also exist for 
quartzite, pegmatites, vermiculite, garnet, vein quartz, chalcedony 
silicides, quartzite sand, 600 million tonnes of deep mined gypsum and 
pearlite.
<P>
The government had decided to close down loss making ore and uranium mines. 
Against an increasing rate of unemployment, galloping inflation and falling 
living standards, miners in the poorly equipped pits staged a series of 
strikes which put considerable pressure on a coalition dependent on trade 
union support.
<P>
Cadmium production hit 232 tonnes in 1992, up from 194 tonnes in the 
previous year. Copper concentrate showed a similar rise, from 243,000 tonnes
in 1991 to 301,000 tonnes in 1992. Only small amounts of silver and gold are 
produced, reaching 1,303 kg and 559 kg respectively in 1992.
<P>
<hr>
<a href="#List"><img src="images/arrowup.gif" alt="Top" align=right border=0></a>
<P>
<center><IMG SRC="images/pinred.gif"> <A HREF="bsmenu.html">Bulgaria Subjects</A></center>
<P>

