<P>
<H3>Social Niceties, Traditions & Taboos</H3>
<P>
Bulgarians are naturally ebullient and hospitable people. It is usual to 
offer your hosts some hospitality at a good restaurant or club. It is not 
always expected that spouses would join the party. Shaking hands is the 
traditional form of greeting.
<P>
