anning, and more.<p>
			
							Check out our formula for determining if you can afford a second home. 	An investment-portfolio work sheet for short-, medium-, and long-term time horizons enables you to calculate the appropriate assets for your income level and investment objecti
ves. You can also determine your risk tolerance by filling out a simple questionnaire.<p>
							
							We realize that you might have questions we have not touched upon in the Solution Series. There are other areas of the Worth OnLine site you can consult. Look in <a href="departments.html">Departments</a>, our virtual file cabinet, for investor res
ources. Also, try our archives. They form the most complete reference source for articles that have appeared in Worth magazine. The Bulletin Boards offer forums for investors to talk to one another about their money questions. <p>
							
							Soon we'll be bringing you a brand new version of the Solution Series, with interactive tools that enable you to customize the formulas to figure out your financial needs down to the dime.
			
