<center> <h1>Worth OnLine Reader Survey</h1> </center>
 <p>
<font size=+1>
We'd like to get to know you better so we can tailor our site to suit your interests and investing needs. Your answers will remain confidential and any information you give us will not be sold to outside parties.
<p>
Please take a moment to answer the following questions:
<p>
<FORM ACTION="/cgi/survey.cgi" METHOD="POST">
<b>WHO ARE YOU?</b><p>
1. Are you <INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q1" VALUE="1">
 male or <INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q1" VALUE="2"> female?

<p>
2. What is your age?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q2" VALUE="1"> 18-24<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q2" VALUE="2"> 25-34<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q2" VALUE="3"> 35-44<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q2" VALUE="4"> 45-49<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q2" VALUE="5"> 50-54<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q2" VALUE="5"> 55-64<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q2" VALUE="6"> 65 and over <br>

<p>

3. What is the highest level of education you have completed?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q3" VALUE="1"> High school graduate or less<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q3" VALUE="2"> Some college<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q3" VALUE="3"> College graduate<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q3" VALUE="4"> Post graduate study/degree<br>
<p>

4. What is your yearly income?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q4" VALUE="1"> Less than $50,000<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q4" VALUE="2"> $50,000 to $99,9999<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q4" VALUE="3"> $100,000 to $249,999<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q4" VALUE="4"> $250,000 to $499,999<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q4" VALUE="5"> $500,000 to $999,999<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q4" VALUE="6"> $1 million +<br>
<p>

5. What is your approximate net worth (including all assets)?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q5" VALUE="1"> Less than $100,000<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q5" VALUE="2"> $100,000 to $499,999<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q5" VALUE="3"> $500,000 to $1 million<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q5" VALUE="4"> $1 million to $4.9 million<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q5" VALUE="5"> $5 million to $9..9 million<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q5" VALUE="6"> $10 million +<br>

<p>

<b>WHAT DO YOU DO? </b>
<p>

1. Are you <INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q6" VALUE="1"> self-employed, or <INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q6" VALUE="2"> do you work for someone else?
<p>

2. What is your employment status?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q7" VALUE="1"> Retired<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q7" VALUE="2"> Unemployed, seeking work<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q7" VALUE="3"> Unemployed, not seeking work<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q7" VALUE="4"> Employed<br>
<p>

3. In which industry are you employed?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="1"> Accounting<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="2"> Banking<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="3"> Communications/ Publishing/ Entertainment<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="4"> Computers/ Software/ Systems<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="5"> Education/ Schools <br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="6"> Financial Services/ Securities <br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="7"> Health Care/ Hospitals<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="8"> Importing/ Trade <br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="9"> Insurance<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="10"> Legal <br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="11"> Manufacturing<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="12"> Nonprofit/ Goverment/ Associations<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="13"> Packaged Goods/ Food<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="14"> Pharmaceuticals <br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="15"> Real Estate<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="16"> Retailing <br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="17"> Transportation<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q8" VALUE="18"> Other<br>
<p>

4. What is your position in your company?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q9" VALUE="1"> Owner/Partner<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q9" VALUE="2"> President, CEO, COO, Chairman of the Board, other company officer<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q9" VALUE="3"> Director, Department Head, Manager<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q9" VALUE="4"> Other  <br>

<p>

5. How many people work in your company?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q10" VALUE="1"> Less than 10<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q10" VALUE="2"> 10-49<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q10" VALUE="3"> 50-99<br>
