<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q10" VALUE="8"> 10,000 or more<br>

<p>


<b>HOW DO YOU INVEST?</b><p>
1. How often do you read Worth magazine?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q11" VALUE="1"> Never<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q11" VALUE="2"> 1-2 times per year<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q11" VALUE="3"> 3-10 times per year<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q11" VALUE="4"> I Subscribe<br>
<p>

2. How many stock transactions have you made in the past 12 months?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q12" VALUE="1">  Zero<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q12" VALUE="2">  1-9<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q12" VALUE="3">   10-24<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q12" VALUE="4">   25-49<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q12" VALUE="5">   50-99<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q12" VALUE="6">   100 or more<br>
<p>

3. Which of the following do you use most frequently?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="1">  Retail bank<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="2"> Private bank<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="3"> Mutual fund rating service<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="4"> Stock rating service<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="5"> Brokerage firm<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="6"> Discount brokerage firm<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="7"> Financial planner or money manager<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="8"> Asset manager<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q13" VALUE="9"> Insurance agent<br>

<p>

4. Do you use online financial services?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q14" VALUE="1"> Yes<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q14" VALUE="2"> No<br>

<p>

5. Which is your primary investment goal?<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q15" VALUE="1"> Retirement<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q15" VALUE="2"> Home/Second Home<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q15" VALUE="3"> Education<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q15" VALUE="4"> Other<br>

<p>
<b>CRITIQUE WORTH ONLINE</b>
<p>
We are always working to improve Worth OnLine. Reader feedback is the most important input we get. Your comments will help us determine the future of Worth OnLine. Please take a few minutes to answer the four questions below.
<p>
1. What are you looking for when you come to Worth OnLine?<br>

<textarea name="like_looking" rows=4 cols=40 wrap=physical>
Tell us here</textarea>
