<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q19" VALUE="1">1
&nbsp;<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q19" VALUE="2">2
&nbsp;<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q19" VALUE="3">3
&nbsp;<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q19" VALUE="4">4
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q19" VALUE="5">5 - best
<p>
4. Specifically, what feature do your like BEST on our site?
<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q18" VALUE="1">Front Page<br>
<INPUT TYPE="radio" NAME="q18" VALUE="2">Archives<br>
