						<a href="Trans012297.html">01/22/97 -- Jack Robinson, manager of the Green Century Balanced Fund</a><br>
						<a href="Trans011597.html">01/15/97 -- Peter Crane, author of "Mutual Fund Investing on the Internet"</a><br>
						<a href="Trans010897.html">01/04/97 -- Ken Kurson, the Worth Advocate</a><br>
					</blockquote>
					</font>
		
		
		
</td><td width=150 valign=top>

<center>
		
	<a href="/index.html">
	<IMG SRC="/imgs/TRANSCRIPTS.gif" border=0 alt="Worth"></a><p>
</center>
<pre>


</pre>
					<b>
					Peter Lynch. Michael Murphy. Elizabeth Bramwell. These are just a few of the guests who have joined Worth OnLine to chat live about money and the markets. Chats currently are limited to our America Online site. But stay tuned for updates on chat availability on the Web! In the meantime, we'll file transcripts of each live event right here. <p>

					</b>
	
		
